Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:07.76,Default,Man1,0,0,0,,{Where's Malik?}Malik đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.01,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,Bị cảm lạnh đang nằm bẹp trên giường.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:17.10,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{The bug going around \Nthis year is a nasty one.}Lỗi xảy ra năm nay đúng là khó chịu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.77,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Just awful, isn't it?}Ghét ghê đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:22.64,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Mind if I take a look at what's inside?}Tôi xem qua được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.30,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{Rouge, would you mind?}Rouge, nhờ cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.46,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{There.}Kéo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.55,Default,Man1,0,0,0,,{Who's got a cold, now?}Ai bị cảm lạnh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:40.03,Default,Man1,0,0,0,,{That's Malik lying over there, isn't it?}Tên đang nằm kia chẳng phải là Malik à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:43.71,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.19,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Oh, Malik!}A, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:49.60,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{How could you have died of a simple cold?!}Sao có thể chết vì bị cảm lạnh chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.12,Default,Man2,0,0,0,,{Enough bullshit!}Đừng có giỡn mặt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.44,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Come, now. I'm being quite serious.}Này này, tao đang nghiêm túc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.45,Default,Man1,0,0,0,,{Just who are you?}Mày là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:07.54,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Who... am...}Là... ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.29,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I?}Nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:12.35,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.93,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.92,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{Take care of this, would you?}Nhờ cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.66,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh, sure.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.20,Default,Staff1,0,0,0,,{Outta the way.}Cản trở quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.70,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Sorry...}Xin lỗi ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:28.69,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry. She's new at this.}Xin lỗi nhé, con bé là người mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.92,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{Come on, Rouge. No spacing out.}Nào Rouge, đừng thơ thẩn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.39,Default,Band Member1,0,0,0,,{There's Sarah's bad habit again.}Lại thói xấu của Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.91,Default,Band Member2,0,0,0,,{Was it really smart to \Ntake in a girl like that?}Nhặt con bé đó ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.37,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.91,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Er...}Ủa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:51.96,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{Here you go.}Của cô đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.38,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh, thank you.}A, cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.48,Default,Staff1,0,0,0,,{Yo, Scar Head! Get this place \Ncleaned up already!}Này Đầu Sẹo! Dọn dẹp lẹ đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.89,Default,Staff1,0,0,0,,{Don't think you can slack off \N'cause you're a Nean!}Đừng nghĩ là Nean thì có thể trốn việc!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.21,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.52,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,Mai lại nhờ cô. Ngủ ngon nhé Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.81,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Same to you, Ms. Sarah.}Vâng, cả cô nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.30,Default,NeanB,0,0,0,,Biến mất rồi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.19,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{I know it was here this morning.}Tôi để đây hồi sáng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.80,Default,NeanB,0,0,0,,{Here, use mine.}Dùng của tôi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:25.91,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{I can't. Then you'll cease to function.}Không được. Cô sẽ ngừng hoạt động mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.71,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{And if that happens, you'll be discarded.}Và sẽ bị xoá bỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.51,Default,Staff2,0,0,0,,{See ya later, rookie.}Gặp sau nhé lính mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.44,Default,NeanB,0,0,0,,{But you need your shot of Nectar \Nbefore the day ends, too.}Nhưng anh cũng cần Nectar trước\N khi ngày hôm nay kết thúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.59,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{Don't worry. I'm sure it's here somewhere.}Đừng lo, nó ở đâu đây thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.25,Default,NeanB,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.19,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.19,Default,Staff2,0,0,0,,{Who's entertaining our star tonight?}Đêm nay ai là ngôi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.18,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{Some hotshot from Panacea.}Ảnh nóng từ Panacea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.21,Default,Staff2,0,0,0,,{Talk about your ideal patron.}Anh tìm được người bảo trợ tuyệt nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.86,Default,Staff2,0,0,0,,{Here's to Sarah Fitzgerald,}Cạn ly vì Sarah Fitzgerald,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:05:01.00,Default,Staff2,0,0,0,,{the diva of Club Canal who's \Nkeeping food on all our tables.}diva của Club Canal, tạo\N công ăn việc làm cho chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.49,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{Where's Kevin, anyway?}Kevin đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.49,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{Something good happen to him or what?}Có chuyện gì vui à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.33,Default,Staff1,0,0,0,,{Check it out!}Nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.17,Default,Staff2,0,0,0,,{Nectar sells for a fortune.}Nectar giá cao lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:16.82,Default,Staff2,0,0,0,,{And when a human uses it, they get a \Ntaste of Heaven on Earth, apparently.}Và khi con người dùng chúng \Nthì phê như lên thiên đường ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.88,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{It's on you if that comes back to bite you.}Có bị phản đừng trách đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.88,Default,Staff1,0,0,0,,{They've all got the Asimov \NCode programmed into 'em.}Chúng đều có chương trình Code Asimov cài vào rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.43,Default,Staff1,0,0,0,,{They can't defy us humans.}Không dám chống lại con người đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:29.67,Default,Staff2,0,0,0,,Nè, nghe nói Nean là điệp viên ngoài hành tinh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:32.96,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,{What, like, Visitors? \NYou actually believe that?}Hả? Cậu tin điều đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.94,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{So what did you think, tweet?}Thế cậu nghĩ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.68,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I don't think it's her.}Tớ nghĩ không phải cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.48,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{State your reasoning.}Lý do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:49.60,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Well... It's just a hunch, really...}Chỉ là... cảm giác thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.22,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{Then it contributes nothing.}Vậy thì không thể khẳng định.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.73,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{Who was that man with her?}Tên đàn ông đi cùng thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:55.81,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{An executive from Panacea. \NI think his name's... Herman...}Giám đốc điều hành Panacea... Tên là Herman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.12,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,Herman Heyward?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.28,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Chính nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.49,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I looked really closely, but...}Tớ đã quan sát kĩ lắm rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.64,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I couldn't see a Nectar intake unit on him.}Nhưng không thể thấy đơn vị hút Nectar trên ông ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.55,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{Just looking won't tell you anything! \NThat's true for you, isn't it?}Nhìn sao biết được! Cậu cũng thế còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.87,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I guess so.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:10.28,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{Tweet! Tweet!}Chíp! Chíp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:14.05,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{You need to stick closer to Sarah \Nand get conclusive proof!}Cậu cần phải bám sát Sarah và tìm bằng chứng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.44,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{Action comes after that, tweet!}Và tìm cách hành động, chíp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:27.13,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{Tweet. I'll be waiting behind \Nthe theater at noon. Tweet.}Chíp. Tớ sẽ chờ sau rạp hát vào buổi trưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:27.99,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{For what?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.16,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{Your regular report.}Báo cáo thường xuyên.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.56,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh...}Ồ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.94,DefaultItalics,Bird (Naomi),0,0,0,,{Self-awareness intact?}Nhận thức còn nguyên không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:32.91,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I think so.}Còn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.83,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Roger!}Rõ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.66,Default,Herman,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.46,Default,SP1,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?!}Cô ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.57,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{A red Gladiator...}Gladiator đỏ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.83,Default,Herman,0,0,0,,{Sarah! Are you hurt?}Sarah! Có bị thương không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.42,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Ow!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.96,Default,NeanC,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}Quý khách ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:19.16,DefaultItalics,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{This is footage taken \Nby an anonymous citizen}Đây là đoạn phim quay bởi một người ẩn danh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:22.27,DefaultItalics,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{of the scene of the murder \Nthat took place in the suburbs.}hiện trường của vụ giết người ở ngoại ô.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:27.00,DefaultItalicsTop,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{The video seems to become \Ndistorted in the vicinity}Đoạn video dường như bị nhiễu 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.29,DefaultItalicsTop,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{of this individual who \Nseems to be the suspect.}ở xung quanh vị trí của nghi phạm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:33.20,DefaultItalicsTop,Specialist,0,0,0,,{There must be some sort \Nof interference in the—}Có vẻ là nó đã bị can thiệp chỉnh sửa--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.59,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{What a pain.}Phiền phức ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.67,Default,Herman,0,0,0,,{Yeah. It's probably the same one.}Ừm, có lẽ là cùng loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.02,Default,Herman,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.21,Default,Herman,0,0,0,,{Yeah, he showed up here, too.}Nó cũng xuất hiện ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.77,Default,NeanB,0,0,0,,{The sender didn't give a name.}Không có tên người gửi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.03,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:58.50,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{Give it back...}Trả lại đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.52,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{Please... give me back... my Nectar!}Xin hãy... trả lại Nectar của tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.01,Default,Staff1,0,0,0,,{What're you on? I dunno \Nwhat you're talkin' about.}Gì thế? Tao có biết gì đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.84,Default,NeanA,0,0,0,,{Please... Please!}Làm ơn! Làm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.61,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Well, that's reality.}Đây là hiện thực nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.61,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hey, I'm here.}Đến rồi nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:42.49,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Um... Who were you again?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.27,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Tweet, tweet.}Chíp chíp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:48.28,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh! The bird's voice!}A, tiếng chim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:57.51,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I had no idea there was an actual \Nperson talking through that bird.}Không ngờ trong con chim có người...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.40,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hmm?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:03.95,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh... I said, I had no idea there was an \Nactual person talking through that bird.}À... Không ngờ trong con chim có người.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:05.42,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hmm?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.14,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I said, I had no idea there was—}À... không ngờ--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:12.50,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{What, is your memory broken?!}Kí ức của cô bị hỏng rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.93,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{So... who are you, exactly?}Vậy... cô là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.17,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I'm Naomi Orthmann. Nice to meet you.}Naomi Orthmann, rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:21.43,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I've been supporting you.}Tôi đã luôn hỗ trợ cô đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.70,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Well, that's kind of you. Um, I'm—}Cảm ơn cô. Tôi là--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:25.66,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I know you.}Biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.06,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Well, thank you.}Vậy cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.53,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Excuse me!}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:36.02,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{An extra-large fried rice, twice-cooked pork,\Nmapo tofu, and two jajangmyeon!}Một cơm chiên lớn, hai thịt heo,\N đậu phụ ma bà và hai jajangmyeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:39.58,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{So, um, where's the bird?}Thế chim đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:41.07,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{It died.}Chết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.58,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh, what a shame.}A, vậy hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:44.18,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{My condolences.}Xin lỗi vì đã hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.83,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Thank you kindly.}Cảm ơn cô đã quan tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.42,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{So, any progress since then?}Thế có tiến triển gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:56.49,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{No. I still don't think Sarah is Viola.}Không. Tôi không nghĩ Sarah là Viola.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:59.17,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it's not her.}Ừm, không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.71,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Sorry to tell you this,}Đáng tiếc,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.40,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{but Sarah Fitzgerald was \Ninjecting herself with Nectar.}nhưng Sarah Fitzgerald đã tiêm Nectar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:12.88,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{She's a Nean, and most likely, \None of the Immortal Nine.}Cô ta là một Nean, và là một trong 9 kẻ bất tử.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.57,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Viola Keane, also known as...}Viola Keane, hay còn gọi là...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.67,Default,Roger,0,0,0,,Viola luyện ngục.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.43,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Confess your sins.}Hãy thú tội của con đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.50,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{Stop that.}Dừng lại đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.91,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{I would've preferred never to see you again.}Nếu được tôi không muốn gặp lại anh đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.50,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Now, that's just cold.}Lạnh lùng quá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.76,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{I need you to keep your promise.}Tôi chỉ cần anh giữ lời hứa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:37.76,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Of course I will. However, \NI ran into a little trouble.}Dĩ nhiên rồi. Nhưng có rắc rối nhỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.28,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{I gave you all the information you needed.}Tôi đã đưa anh tất cả thông tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:41.85,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Yes, you did!}Phải phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:46.02,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Oh, you went so far as to \Ntaint your own body—no,}Thậm chí cô còn dùng cả cơ thể xinh đẹp-- không,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:50.12,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{you put your body on the line \Nto get me that information!}liều lĩnh dùng cơ thể để lấy thông tin cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:54.15,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{And all the Nectar was taken right out \Nfrom under me. What a massive failure.}Và tất cả Nectar đã bị cướp đi trước mặt tôi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:58.51,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm sorry to hear that, \Nbut it's not my concern.}Xin lỗi, nhưng chẳng liên quan đến tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:01.28,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{It was the red guy who took it.}Kẻ lấy là tên màu đỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:06.91,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Yes! The archenemy of us Alters, \Nthe one who killed Nius and Achillus!}Phải! Kẻ thù không đội trời chung của\N Alters chúng ta, kẻ đã giết Nius và Achillus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:10.00,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{The very same red Gladiator!}Gladiator đỏ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.70,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{He came after me, too.}Hắn cũng đã đến chỗ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.82,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{What?! Thank goodness you're safe!}May mà cô vẫn an toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.17,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{Keep your promise!}Mau giữ lời hứa đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.78,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{You have my sympathy.}Tôi đồng cảm với cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.90,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{If this job had been a success,}Nếu công việc lần này thành công,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:24.04,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{you could have cut ties with us Alters.}cô sẽ chấm dứt với Alters bọn tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.93,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{But that was only a fleeting dream.}Nhưng đó chỉ là giấc mộng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.59,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,Giallon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:33.26,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{One of our own, Silvia, suspects \Nthat you leaked that information.}Một người trong bọn tôi, Silvia,\Nnghi ngờ cô đã làm lộ thông tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.44,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{She does?}Cô ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:38.90,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I insisted that you were innocent, but...}Tôi đã khẳng định cô vô tội nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.25,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,Tôi tí nữa bị giết đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.62,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{That's just the thing.}Đúng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:46.53,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I want to protect you, even if it \Nmeans defying the organization.}Tôi muốn bảo vệ cô, dù phải chống lại tổ chức.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.00,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Has anything odd happened lately?}Gần đây có gì kì lạ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.81,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Anyone unfamiliar tried to approach you?}Có kẻ nào kì lạ cố tiếp cận cô không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:14.24,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{He who makes the first move wins.}Kẻ nào hành động trước sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.43,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Aren't you gonna eat?}Cô có ăn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.80,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{This is enough.}Vậy đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.41,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:31.79,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{What?! What, what, what?!}Hả? Ủa? Ơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:37.82,DefaultItalics,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{This is the footage of the suspect \Nat the scene of last night's murder}Đây là đoạn phim quay lại\N nghi phạm vụ giết người đêm qua,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.55,DefaultItalics,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{with as much of the static \Nremoved as possible.}đã được loại bỏ nhiễu nhiều nhất có thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.33,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Who's that?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.11,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Can't you tell?}Nhìn mà không biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.04,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I don't recognize him.}Tôi không nhớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.10,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{That's okay.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.73,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I've got a pretty good idea.}Tôi có ý tưởng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:54.00,DefaultItalics,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{It has been pointed out that \Nthe suspect closely resembles}Người ta đã chỉ ra rằng nghi phạm rất giống
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:58.09,DefaultItalics,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{the suspect spotted at the \Nmurder of Dr. Roy Junghardt,}kẻ đã sát hại tiến sĩ Roy Junghardt,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:00.84,DefaultItalics,Newscaster,0,0,0,,{a researcher at a well-known \NNean research lab.}một nhà nghiên cứu nổi tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.83,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Come on, eat some meat.}Thôi thôi, ăn thịt đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.01,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Tôi ăn vậy thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.14,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.74,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{Would you mind accompanying me tonight?}Đêm nay đi cùng tôi chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.47,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{I crossed this bridge to come here.}Tôi đã đi qua cây cầu này để đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:28.27,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{I abandoned my real self from the past \Non the other side of this bridge,}Bỏ lại bản thân quá khứ ở bên kia cầu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.90,Default,Sarah,0,0,0,,{hoping to become a brand-new me.}hi vọng được sống thật với bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:37.08,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{What is one's "real self," I wonder?}Cái nào mới là bản thân thực sự?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.95,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Viola Keane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:48.51,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{I liked you. I really did.}Tôi đã từng thích cô. Thật đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:52.00,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Neans can't kill people.}Nean không thể giết người.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.24,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{We're not your standard Neans.}Bọn tôi không phải Nean bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:59.00,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{You're the same as us, aren't you?}Cô cũng thế nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.68,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Oops.}Úi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.32,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Was that the wrong one?}Nhầm người à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.51,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{You're... Giallon?!}Anh... là Giallon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:34.71,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Well, silly me. \NI was certain she was the one.}Tôi tưởng chắc chắn là cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.22,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{I forgot about your ability to mimic.}Quên mất năng lực bắt chước của anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.59,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{So the one who attacked me then...}Vậy kẻ tấn công tôi khi đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:43.13,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Yep! It was me!}Phải! Là tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.26,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Hell Giallon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:49.43,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{That's him? Whew, scary.}Là hắn à? Sợ quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.64,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Why did you attack me?}Tại sao lại tấn công tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.46,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Why, out of the kindness of my heart!}Tại sao? Vì lòng tốt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.87,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I just thought I'd give you a little push.}Tôi định thúc đẩy cô một chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.90,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{You know I would never kill you!}Chứ làm sao tôi dám giết cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.68,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I just stopped right before!}Tôi đã dừng ngay đúng lúc mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:05.46,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Oh, I'm such a kind man!}Quả là người đàn ông tốt bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.34,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I mean, you were hesitating!}Vì cô do dự!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:10.32,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Couldn't you have killed that cutie yourself?}Cô có dám xuống tay với con bé dễ thương đó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:12.03,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{I could have.}Có.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.03,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{I had my doubts. \NThat's why I stepped up to—}Nói thế ai chả nói được. Thế nên tôi--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.04,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Rouge wasn't the red Gladiator!}Rouge không phải Gladiator đỏ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.89,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{She had nothing to do with this!}Con bé không liên quan gì cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:22.55,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Are you sure about that? She knew your name,}Cô chắc chứ? Nó biết tên cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:23.55,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,Viola.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:28.39,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Well, she was probably an agent of Aletheia. \NJust one of their dogs.}Có lẽ nó là đặc vụ của Aletheia,\N một con chó của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:31.77,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Killing her was just the right thing to do!}Giết nó là chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.85,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Well, I certainly didn't expect this!}Thật không ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.33,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Gosh, this sure is fun!}Vui quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.40,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{But this is as far as I go.}Nhưng đến đây thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.00,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{You said earlier that you \Ncould've killed her.}Cô đã nói lúc nãy là có thể giết nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.11,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{From now on, you're the star...}Từ giờ, sân khấu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.51,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{and it's showtime!}là của cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:14.80,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Take her out and keep on singing \Nto your heart's content!}Hãy hạ nó và tiếp tục cất vang giọng hát đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.49,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{And with that, adieu, Viola!}Giờ thì, adieu, Viola!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.36,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Before I kill you, tell me your name.}Trước khi giết, có thể nói tên không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.87,Default,MR,0,0,0,,Metal Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:50.52,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{I am one of the Immortal Nine,}Ta là một trong 9 kẻ bất tử,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.68,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Purgatory Viola!}Viole luyện ngục!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:02.61,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Not bad.}Không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.29,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Don't evade her!}Đừng né!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.29,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:29.00,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{If you take just a few more hits, \NI can analyze her!}Nhận thêm vài đòn để tôi phân tích.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.77,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Why did you kill Nius and Achillus?}Tại sao cô lại giết Nius và Achillus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.52,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Why are you after us?}Tại sao lại nhắm vào bọn ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.15,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Just who are you?!}Cô là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.37,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{She's using ion acceleration \Non part of her arm.}Sử dụng gia tốc ion thông qua phần trên cánh tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.87,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{And they're equipped with \Nhigh-frequency blades, too?}Và nó trang bị thêm những lưỡi dao tần số cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:04.10,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{All I wanted to do was sing!}Tôi chỉ muốn được hát.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.35,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{I only wanted to be happy!}Chỉ muốn được hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.55,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Why is that so wrong?!}Tại sao điều đó lại sai trái?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:13.88,Default,MR,0,0,0,,{Are you done, Naomi?!}Xong chưa Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.88,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Just sent it off!}Đang gửi đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.85,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Cheeky brat!}Con nhãi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.57,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{Tell me!}Nói tôi nghe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.82,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{How are we different from humans?!}Chúng ta khác gì con người?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.38,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{I will live! I won't die!}Tôi sẽ sống! Sẽ không chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:53.88,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Your pressure resistance is at breaking point!\NYour outer shell's gonna melt!}Sắp đến giới hạn rồi! Vỏ ngoài sẽ tan chảy đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:57.97,Default,Viola,0,0,0,,{This ends now!}Kết thúc rồi!
